cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR

This paper deals with the annotation and analysis of multimodal discourse in the domain of cooking recipes, which involves both text and images. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and understanding. The use of images also suggests a possible fit with cs.CV (Computer Vision), which deals with image analysis and recognition. The paper also involves the use of crowd-sourcing, which suggests a possible fit with cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper's focus on understanding and generation of multimodal documents suggests a possible fit with cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
